## **Implementation Decisions**

---

### **Architecture**

#### **Frontend**


| Concern              | Tool                     | Notes                                                                                                                                                               |
| -------------------- | ------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| Framework            | HTMX + Jinja2            | Server-rendered HTML; ideal for paper submission, listings, and navigation.                                                                                         |
| Styling              | Tailwind CSS + DaisyUI   | Pre-built components: modals, cards, carousels.                                                                                                                     |
| Client-side logic    | Hyperscript              | Timers, counters, DOM manipulation. Acceptable for a small solo project.                                                                                            |
| LLM streaming        | Server-Sent Events (SSE) | Replaces WebSockets. One-directional token stream; simpler FastAPI implementation via StreamingResponse, no connection manager needed, transparent through proxies. |
| Settings persistence | localStorage             | Replaces cookies for UI state (dark mode, font size, spacing).                                                                                                      |


> **Note:** SSE was chosen over WebSockets because the feedback stream is strictly server-to-client. SSE requires no protocol upgrade, reconnects automatically, and is implemented in FastAPI with a single `StreamingResponse`. WebSockets would add connection lifecycle complexity for no benefit at MVP scale.

#### **Template Structure**

```
templates/
├── base.html          # Layout with HTMX, Tailwind, DaisyUI
├── papers/
│   ├── index.html     # Paper grid (sortable)
│   └── show.html      # Carousel + chapters
├── reading.html       # Reading phase (timer, blur, countdown)
└── writing.html       # Writing phase (word counter, timer, SSE feedback)
```

#### **Backend**


| Concern       | Choice                                               |
| ------------- | ---------------------------------------------------- |
| Framework     | FastAPI (Python)                                     |
| Database      | PostgreSQL 15+ (self-hosted)                         |
| Deployment    | Docker Compose                                       |
| Paper parsing | Docling (native arXiv support)                       |
| LLM           | Mistral API (model pinned to `mistral-small-latest`) |
| Streaming     | FastAPI `StreamingResponse` (SSE)                    |


