### **API Endpoints**


| Endpoint                                  | Method | Description                                                                            |
| ----------------------------------------- | ------ | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| `/papers`                                 | POST   | Submit an arXiv URL for processing.                                                    |
| `/papers`                                 | GET    | List all papers (grid view, sortable).                                                 |
| `/papers/{id}/chapters`                   | GET    | List all chapters for a paper (carousel view).                                         |
| `/papers/{id}/chapter/{chapter_id}/read`  | GET    | Load the reading phase.                                                                |
| `/papers/{id}/chapter/{chapter_id}/write` | GET    | Load the writing phase.                                                                |
| `/summaries`                              | POST   | Submit a user summary. Triggers SSE feedback stream.                                   |
| `/summaries/export`                       | GET    | Export summaries as TXT or Markdown.                                                   |
| `/feedback/{summary_id}`                  | GET    | **SSE endpoint** — streams LLM feedback tokens. Replaces WebSocket endpoint from v1.0. |


> **Note:** The WebSocket endpoint `/ws/feedback/{summary_id}` has been replaced by a plain GET SSE endpoint `/feedback/{summary_id}`. On the client, this is consumed via `new EventSource('/feedback/' + summaryId)`. No library or connection manager is required.

