## **Out of Scope (MVP)**

- Skill development features: progressive difficulty, guided tutorials.
- Retention measurement: no quizzes or spaced repetition.
- Vim keybindings.
- Adjustable writing timer (fixed at `max(2× reading, 3 min)`).
- Cloud hosting (self-hosted only).
- Authentication and cross-device sync.
- Retry logic for failed API calls (e.g., Mistral rate limits).
- Multi-source support (arXiv only; no PDF uploads, DOIs, or other repositories).

