## **Glossary**


| Term                  | Definition                                                                                               |
| --------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **arXiv**             | Open-access repository of scientific papers (primarily CS/ML for this app).                              |
| **Docling**           | Library for parsing and structuring scientific documents.                                                |
| **LLM**               | Large Language Model (Mistral API for summarization/feedback).                                           |
| **HTMX**              | Library for dynamic HTML updates without writing JavaScript.                                             |
| **Hyperscript**       | Lightweight scripting language for client-side logic.                                                    |
| **DaisyUI**           | Tailwind CSS component library.                                                                          |
| **SSE**               | Server-Sent Events — HTTP-based one-way server-to-client stream. Used for feedback token streaming.      |
| **WebSocket**         | Bidirectional protocol. Considered and rejected for MVP; SSE is sufficient.                              |
| **reference_summary** | LLM-generated summary stored per chapter at processing time; used as the grading baseline.               |
| **attempt_number**    | Monotonically increasing counter on `user_summaries` tracking how many times a chapter has been retried. |
